  "text": "• In certain cases when the n i 's have many factors in common, it is possible to construct indecomposable P n 1 ,...,n k -tilings of minimal period M = lcm(n 1 , . . . , n k ) [CITATION_1] . We do this asymptotical computation at the end of the section.",
